  <summary>3/7/2002--Introduced.
Military Families Unification Act of 2002 - Exempts certain spouses and children of qualifying active duty Philippine enlistees in the United States Navy from prohibitions under the Immigration and Nationality Act on: (1) admission based on unlawful presence; or (2) relief based upon failure to voluntarily depart.Provides such aliens with work authorization.</summary>
